OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FGranada correspondent Elaine Willcox
OL,7,Fspeaks to North West mums and health
OL,8,Fprofessionals campaigning for urgent
OL,9,Fchange to make maternity services
OL,10,Fsafer.
OL,12,FA mother from Lancashire has told how
OL,13,Fa midwife broke down in tears on her
OL,14,Fbed and apologised for the poor care
OL,15,Fshe had received after giving birth at
OL,16,FBlackpool Victoria Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
