OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FEleanor Marshall, from Lytham,
OL,7,Fsuffered post-natal depression after
OL,8,Fher birthing experience at the
OL,9,Fhospital, one of 12 trusts
OL,10,Finvestigated in a national review of
OL,11,Fmaternity services by Baroness Amos,
OL,12,Fpublished today.
OL,14,FThe Amos report gathered the views of
OL,15,Fmore than 450 families and received
OL,16,Fmore 10,500 responses to a public call
OL,17,Ffor evidence, while 9,000 staff also
OL,18,Fcontributed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FEleanor said: "I wasn't with my
OL,7,Fdaughter - she had to go to the
OL,8,Fneonatal for support. I was told that
OL,9,FI wouldn't be able to see her until
OL,10,Fthe following afternoon, because there
OL,11,Fwas no-one there to take me.
OL,13,F"I'd gone 'over' on pain relief by
OL,14,Fhours. I had a midwife draw the
OL,15,Fcurtain around me and just break down
OL,16,Fon my bed and just apologise, saying,
OL,17,F'I'm so sorry'."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FEleanor now works as a hypno-birthing
OL,7,Fspecialist and doula - a non-medical
OL,8,Fprofessional who provides support to
OL,9,Fpeople through a significant life
OL,10,Fexperience, usually childbirth.
OL,12,FBaroness Amos recommends the creation
OL,13,Fof a Maternity Commissioner and
OL,14,Fchanges to the triage system to drive
OL,15,Fthrough change.
OL,17,FThe Morecambe Bay Trust, also
OL,18,Fhighlighted in her report, insists
OL,19,Fprogress is being made towards safer
OL,20,Fmaternity services, but apologised to
OL,21,Ffamilies for the pain they had caused.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,F"We've worked really really hard to
OL,7,Freduce the vacancy rate across
OL,8,Fmaternity services to do everything we
OL,9,Fpossibly can to ensure that we have
OL,10,Fthe right staffing levels for the
OL,11,Fdemand that we face," said Chief
OL,12,FExecutive Steve Williamson.
OL,14,F"We've recently expanded our triage
OL,15,Fservice, so now mums right across
OL,16,FMorecambe Bay have a single point of
OL,17,Faccess 24 hours a day, 365 days a year
OL,18,Ffor any concern that they might have
OL,19,Fabout their maternity journey."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FBut safer birthing campaigner Rachael
OL,7,FMcGrath said, at the moment, "at least
OL,8,F30,000 women a year" were being
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with Post Traumatic Stress
OL,10,FDisorder within 12 months of having
OL,11,Ftheir baby.
OL,13,FRachael suffered a life-threatening
OL,14,Fhaemorrhage at the Countess of Chester
OL,15,FHospital, resulting in one of her
OL,16,Ftwins being starved of oxygen.
OL,18,FShe now calls for change with the
OL,19,FBirth Trauma Association, whose
OL,20,Fmembers have risen from 3,000 to
OL,21,F20,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FShe also wants racist staff
OL,7,Fhighlighted in the report to be sacked.
OL,9,F"We need to weed out the bad apples.
OL,10,FThere are some, because there are
OL,11,Fmany, many reports that come into the
OL,12,FBTA of women who are subjected to real
OL,13,Fcruelty from healthcare professionals,
OL,14,Fand that is unacceptable in any walk
OL,15,Fof life," she added.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, registered nurses training
OL,18,Fas midwives in Salford are already
OL,19,Facting on Baroness Amos's
OL,20,Frecommendations, calling out
OL,21,Fdiscrimination and poor care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FLisa Bacon, Head of Midwifery at
OL,7,FSalford University, said: "It's
OL,8,Foutrageous and it's it's
OL,9,Fheartbreaking. But all our student
OL,10,Fmidwives undertake an anti-racist
OL,11,Ftraining, active bystander training.
OL,13,F"Everybody that should be standing up
OL,14,Fand saying, this is wrong.
OL,16,F"We will embed all recommendations
OL,17,Finto our midwifery education."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
