OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782854302
OL,3,CMum tells of tearful midwife saying
OL,4,C'sorry' for poor care
OL,6,FThe midwives of the future say they
OL,7,Fwant to rebuild trust and pride in
OL,8,Ftheir profession.JBut with budget cuts
OL,9,Fthey say they also need a guarantee of
OL,10,Fjobs to make change happen for
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
